<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بابُ النّونِ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٨٦٤٧]</span> عَمرُو بنُ نَافعٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٨٦٤٨]</span> عَمرُو بنُ نَصرٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>قولَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قالَهُ حَسنُ بنُ عُمرَ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>، عنْ جريرٍ، عنِ الحَكمِ بنِ مَسلمةَ السَّعديِّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٨٦٤٩]</span> عَمرُو بنُ أبي نُعَيمَةَ المعَافِريُّ <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عنْ أَبي عُثمانَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>رَوى عَنهُ بَكرُ بنُ عَمرٍو.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>المِصريُّ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
